<para style="q1">

<verse number="17" style="v" />The sacrifices of God are a broken spirit.</para>

<para style="q1">You, God, will not despise a broken and a contrite heart.</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="18" style="v" />Do good in your good pleasure to Zion;</para>

<para style="q1">rebuild the walls of Jerusalem.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="19" style="v" />Then will you delight in the sacrifices of righteousness,</para>

<para style="q1">in burnt offerings and whole burnt offerings;</para>

<para style="q1">then our people will offer bulls on your altar.</para>
